of reprisal massacres.

521
00:36:08,520 --> 00:36:10,880
Will the U.N. intervene
to stop the bloodshed?

522
00:36:10,960 --> 00:36:13,920
We're here as peacekeepers.
not as peacemakers.

523
00:36:14,000 --> 00:36:16,560
My orders are
not to intervene.

524
00:36:17,480 --> 00:36:19,280
- Excuse me.
- Thank you, Colonel.

525
00:36:20,000 --> 00:36:21,040
Here. Over here.

526
00:36:21,040 --> 00:36:24,080
Listen, I got us a car.
but we gotta move now.

527
00:36:24,800 --> 00:36:26,400
We're not allowed
to do that, Jack.

528
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:29,680
David, the shit's going down outside
these walls. We gotta cover it.

529
00:36:29,760 --> 00:36:32,720
We're not leaving the hotel grounds
unless we have an armored car.

530
00:36:32,840 --> 00:36:34,920
- That's the ground rules.
- The ground rules?

531
00:36:34,920 --> 00:36:36,720
Where do you think we are.
fucking Wimbledon?

532
00:36:36,760 --> 00:36:41,560
We cover the story from here
until we get the proper vehicles, Jack.

